               throws info.kgeorgiy.java.advanced.implementor.ImplerException
        Implements a class Output file is @param classname + Impl.java Puts output file to @param root / @param className package initialises functions with empty HashSet initialises classname with @param className
        Specified by:
        implement in interface info.kgeorgiy.java.advanced.implementor.Impler
